OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773191771
OL,3,CGuernsey silver medallist Lucy Beere
OL,4,Cdrops out of Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FGuernsey bowler Lucy Beere has pulled
OL,7,Fout of the 2026 Commonwealth Games in
OL,8,FGlasgow, after she says she felt
OL,9,F"increasingly isolated" by the
OL,10,Feligibility and selection process.
OL,12,FBeere, 43, won a silver medal at the
OL,13,F2022 Games, the island's first podium
OL,14,Ffinish since Graham Le Maitre and
OL,15,FAdrian Breton won bronze in 1994 in
OL,16,Fthe rapid fire pistol.
OL,18,FShe says withdrawing has been "one of
OL,19,Fthe most difficult decisions" of her
OL,20,Fcareer.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
