FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773191771
OL,3,CGuernsey silver medallist Lucy Beere
OL,4,Cdrops out of Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FIn a statement sent to ITV News, Beere
OL,7,Fadds: "Over a number of months, I
OL,8,Ffound myself navigating a complex and,
OL,9,Fat times, unclear eligibility process.
OL,11,F"After a prolonged period seeking
OL,12,Fclarification regarding my
OL,13,Feligibility, it was ultimately
OL,14,Fconfirmed that I was eligible to
OL,15,Ftrial. However, by that stage, the
OL,16,Fprocess had taken a significant
OL,17,Fpersonal toll.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773191771
OL,3,CGuernsey silver medallist Lucy Beere
OL,4,Cdrops out of Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F"There were also issues surrounding
OL,7,Fpersonal arrangements that had
OL,8,Fpreviously been accommodated at the
OL,9,Flast Games but were not supported on
OL,10,Fthis occasion.
OL,12,F"The combination of these factors left
OL,13,Fme feeling increasingly isolated and
OL,14,Funcertain about my ability to
OL,15,Fparticipate in the selection process
OL,16,Fin a healthy and positive environment."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773191771
OL,3,CGuernsey silver medallist Lucy Beere
OL,4,Cdrops out of Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FIn 2022, Guernsey won two medals at a
OL,7,FCommonwealth Games for the first time
OL,8,Fsince 1986, after Beere's second-place
OL,9,Ffinish and Alastair Chalmers winning
OL,10,Fbronze in the men's 400m hurdles.
OL,12,FBeere is one of four silver medallists
OL,13,Ffor the island since 1970, and was one
OL,14,Fof the Bailiwick's best hopes for
OL,15,Fglory in the upcoming Games.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773191771
OL,3,CGuernsey silver medallist Lucy Beere
OL,4,Cdrops out of Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FShe explains: "While I understand that
OL,7,Felite sport can be challenging and
OL,8,Fthat difficult decisions are often
OL,9,Fpart of high-performance pathways, the
OL,10,Fsituation ultimately impacted me both
OL,11,Fmentally and physically.
OL,13,F"For that reason, and after careful
OL,14,Freflection, I made the decision to
OL,15,Fwithdraw from the selection process.
OL,17,F"I sincerely hope that my experience
OL,18,Fmay assist in improving processes and
OL,19,Fclarity for athletes in future
OL,20,FCommonwealth Games cycles.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773191771
OL,3,CGuernsey silver medallist Lucy Beere
OL,4,Cdrops out of Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F"I would like to wish Team Guernsey
OL,7,Fevery success at the upcoming Games
OL,8,Fand hope the team achieves outstanding
OL,9,Fresults."
